@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.42 + tmp + 0.30)) - ((tmp + 0.22 + tmp + 0.01) + 0.80))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.48) / wp.abs(tmp + 0.26)) - wp.abs((v1 + 0.59 / tmp + 0.73)))
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.38) - (0.83 - (v1 + 0.81 / tmp + 0.54)))
    data[tid] = v0
